  <p>A key takeaway from this sensitivity analysis is the impact of American Tower's massive debt load (approx. $45B). The Enterprise Value is quite high, but subtracting this debt severely penalizes the final Equity Value, making the model highly sensitive to the discount rate and required growth.</p>

